title: White House Said to Consider Pushing Congress on Dealing With TikTok
description: In a strategy shift, the Biden administration is increasingly pointing to Congress to give it more legal power to deal with TikTok and other technology that could expose Americans’ sensitive data to China.

title: How Some Gen Z Instagram Users Post to Facebook: Unwittingly
description: Teenagers and young adults are flummoxed. The reason it keeps happening involves an online prompt and product design.
